            "heading": "> Step 1 - Exfoliation with Copper Crusted Silk Cocoons",
            "description": "<p>Soak a Copper-Crusted Silk Cocoon in warm water for about a minute. Slip it onto your forefinger and gently exfoliate your freshly cleansed face in circular motions, focusing on areas prone to buildup. Use 1–2x/week.</p>",
